35
00:05:25,133 --> 00:05:35,349
If art, say a movie, must carry a message --

36
00:05:35,469 --> 00:05:43,673
a message for humanity -- and if every such testament should also have a message,

37
00:05:43,793 --> 00:05:46,234
then I would like to formulate my "message" right away.

38
00:05:46,354 --> 00:05:51,539
Most of all, I would like to impart that it's necessary to hope and to believe,

39
00:05:51,659 --> 00:05:59,588
that even very bad situations can turn around.

40
00:05:59,708 --> 00:06:04,253
I will show that in my, and then in Sima's and my life

41
00:06:04,373 --> 00:06:07,912
many misfortunes turned into incredible, amazing happiness, richness,

42
00:06:08,032 --> 00:06:15,961
I will try to emphasize this, to show that one needn't despair.

43
00:06:16,081 --> 00:06:22,500
Because I know that these days there is much despair in people's souls.

44
00:06:22,620 --> 00:06:30,732
